pullrequest.title: ready for detailed lidar spec input

content.raw: I put plugin values for the two lidars \(16 and 32\) into the Technical Guide document.  Here is what I’m proposing for the two variants.  Would be good to test with both to make sure there aren’t any showstoppers.  Maybe even run a demo with two of the 32 beam lidars on the wam-v to see if that is feasible?
